---
<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Text Content (Left) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-800 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">About taxomade</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">Your partner for relocation and taxes in Southern Europe.</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
          <p>We are Leonard and Manoli, the founders of taxomade. We know from our own experience how complicated, expensive, and stressful moving to a new country as a remote worker or freelancer can be. Language barriers, confusing tax laws, and slow bureaucracy often get in the way of a smooth start.</p>
          <p>That’s why we built taxomade. We created the service we wish we had when we moved: A simple, digital-first partner that handles your visa, tax registration, and ongoing bookkeeping entirely for you.</p>
          <p>We work with trusted local accountants to give you a transparent, affordable, and fully remote experience. You focus on your work and life under the Mediterranean sun – we take care of the paperwork.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Profile/Steckbrief -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">At a glance</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mt-0.5 mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 block text-sm">Focus</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Freelancers & Remote Workers</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mt-0.5 mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 block text-sm">Operations</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">100% Digital & English-speaking</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mt-0.5 mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 block text-sm">Mission</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Making bureaucracy simple.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image (Right) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-800 rounded-2xl transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 opacity-10"></div>
        <img src="/images/founders.png" alt="Leonard and Jannik, Founders of taxomade" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl relative z-10 w-full h-auto object-cover" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
